 a try, next time!</p><div style="clear:both"></div><div class="reply"> <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/food/problem-eating-meat/?replytocom=14317#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-14317", "14317", "respond", "4412")'>Reply</a></div><div class="fix"></div></div><div class="fix"></div></div><ul class='children'><li class="comment byuser comment-author-Ayngelina bypostauthor odd alt depth-3" id="li-comment-14327"> <a name="comment-14327"></a><div class="comment-container"><div class="comment-head"><div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/4becf0b7984bb629afd7809fc46987a0?s=37&amp;d=blank&amp;r=G' class='photo avatar avatar-37 photo' height='37' width='37' /></div> <span class="name"><span style="">Ayngelina</span></span> <span class="date">on the July 16, 2011 remarked</span> <span class="edit"></span> <span class="perma"><a href="http://www.baconismagic.ca/food/problem-eating-meat/#comment-14327" title="Direct link to this comment">#</a></span><div class="fix"></div></div><div class="comment-entry"  id="comment-14327"><div style="padding:10px 8px 3px 10px; background-color: #FFFFE0;"><p>What countries would you recommend, I just ate a ton of it in Latin America.</p></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div class="reply"> <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/food/problem-eating-meat/?replytocom=14327#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-14327", "14327", "respond", "4412")'>Reply</a></div><div class="fix"></div></div><div class="fix"></div></div></li></ul></li><li class="comment byuser comment-author-Ayngelina bypostauthor even depth-2" id="li-comment-14330"> <a name="comment-14330"></a><div class="comment-container"><div class="comment-head"><div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/4becf0b7984bb629afd7809fc46987a0?s=37&amp;d=blank&amp;r=G' class='photo avatar avatar-37 photo' height='37' width='37' /></div> <span class="name"><span style="">Ayngelina</span></span> <span class="da